External knowledge:
- 'most recently played tracks' refers to tracks with the most recent 'last played' date; 
- 'highest play count' refers to the maximum number of times a track has been played among all tracks with the same 'last played' date;
- 'top 10 most played' refers to the tracks with the highest play count among the most recently played tracks, limited to 10 results.

